Tests (10 total):
1. CasinoAudioManager instantiates without throwing
2. init() creates an AudioContext
3. onWin(150, 25) — genuine win, does NOT call onNearMiss
4. onWin(20, 25) — net loss (LDW case), calls onNearMiss and NOT win jingle
5. onWin(0, 25) — zero return, plays loss sound (not near-miss, not win)
6. setEnabled(false) then onWin — no audio methods called
7. playSurgeRise(0) — starts Shepard generator
8. playSurgeRise(3) — calls step() on generator
9. stopSurgeRise() — stops Shepard generator
10. destroy() — cleans up without throwing

The key assertion for test 4 (LDW prevention) is the most important — verify that when winAmount (20) <= betAmount (25), the near-miss path is taken and the win path is NOT.

---

Write all 4 files completely in this order: audioConfig.ts, ShepardToneGenerator.ts, CasinoAudioManager.ts, CasinoAudioManager.test.ts.
